20\" data-width=\"280\" data-show-social-context=\"false\" data-show-metadata=\"false\"></div>\r\n<br/>\r\nA1mela.com is UK based, and we act as a directory system to help connect UK supplier and service providers, for Asian / Indian weddings and events, with potential clients.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nWhen arranging a wedding or another event such as a Birthday, Festival, Anniversary, or some other event, it\'s often difficult to for potential clients to connect with the suppliers and service providers they require for their event. Our feature rich search will allow anyone planning an Asian / Indian wedding or event, to search for suppliers and service providers they require to make it a success. You can also add your event details & date for free, so that suppliers can browse and ensure your requirements are met.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nSuppliers and service providers can connect with potential clients by adding their depth company profile. Add descriptive text explaining everything you offer and the customer should choose you, as well as images, videos, categories and much more to allow potential clients to find you. \r\n<br/><br/>\r\nWhether you are a venue, caterer. DJ, event organiser, or any other supplier or service provider, add an in-depth profile and take advantage of the special lockdown and go-live offer now!\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nPlease read the <a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/faq\">FAQ</a> for further information.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nTo contact us to give feedback, advertising queries, or any other reason, please click <a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/contact\">here </a>.\r\n<br/>'),(78555,1,21788,''),(78556,1,21789,'Contact Name'),(78557,1,21790,''),(78558,1,21791,'Contact Number/email'),(78559,1,21792,''),(78560,1,21793,'Company Description'),(78579,1,21812,''),(78580,1,21813,'Other links'),(78581,1,21814,'Settings'),(78563,1,21796,''),(78564,1,21797,'Categories'),(78634,1,21867,'Dancers'),(78633,1,21866,'Singers'),(78585,1,21818,'Here are your latest matches. Please ope