tps://www.a1mela.com/faq\"><span class=\"ow_ic_gear_wheel\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">2. I already have a website, so how would it help to list anything on www.a1events.com as well?</span></a></li></ul>\r\n<br/>\r\nWe aim to be the global source for Indian/Asian wedding and events. People usually prefer to come to a single website where they can find the supplier they are looking for. Similarly, someone looking for video clips might try YouTube first. From our website you can include a link to your website, facebook and other pages. Since your profile will be visible to search engines, you can add a link to your website which may help its ranking. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"ow_content_menu clearfix\">\r\n 	   <li class=\"_preference  active\" style=\"width:100%; \"><a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/faq\"><span class=\"ow_ic_gear_wheel\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">3. What kind of company profiles can be listed?</span></a></li></ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\nAlmost anyone that supplies or provides a service to the Asian/Indian wedding and events market. For example, venues owner, catering companies, DJ, choreographers, singers, magicians, toastmasters, florists and many others.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"ow_content_menu clearfix\">\r\n 	   <li class=\"_preference  active\" style=\"width:100%; \"><a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/faq\"><span class=\"ow_ic_gear_wheel\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">4. Can Bride/Groom register on your site?</span></a></li></ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\nYes Bride/Grooms and anyone organising an any event can register on our site. And we will have special tools for them to communicate with the suppliers and service providers.<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"ow_content_menu clearfix\">\r\n 	   <li class=\"_preference  active\" style=\"width:100%; \"><a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/faq\"><span class=\"ow_ic_gear_wheel\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">5. I have forgotten my password\r\n</span></a></li></ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\nPlease use the <a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/forgot-password\" target=\"blank\">Forgot Password link </a> to have the activation code sent to you so that you can reset your password.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"ow_content_menu clearfix\">\r\n 	  <li class=\"_preference  active\" style=\"width:100%; \"><a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/faq\"><span class=\"ow_ic_gear_wheel\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">6. How do I advertise on your website?\r\n</span></a></li></ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\nAdvertising options will be available in future. For now, please submit your advertising request via the Contact Us link on the top right of the page.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"ow_content_menu clearfix\">\r\n 	   <li class=\"_preference  active\" style=\"width:100%; \"><a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/faq\"><span class=\"ow_ic_gear_wheel\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">7. How can I get in touch with the website administrator for any questions or suggestions I have?\r\n</span></a></li></ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\nPlease use the <a href=\"https://www.a1mela.com/contact\">Contact Us link </a> to contact us.'),(78614,1,21847,'groups+meta_keywords_group_users'),(78615,1,21848,'groups+meta_keywords_groups_page'),(78616,1,21849,'groups+meta_keywords_user_groups'),(78617,1,21850,'groups+meta_keywords_latest'),(78618,1,21851,'groups+meta_keywords_most_popular'),(78619,1,21852,'photo+meta_keywords_photo_view'),(78620,1,21853,'photo+meta_keywords_user_albums'),(78621,1,21854,'photo+meta_keywords_user_photos'),(78622,1,21855,'photo+meta_keywords_user_album'),(78623,1,21856,'photo+meta_keywords_photo_list'),(78624,1,21857,'photo+meta_keywords_tagged_list'),(78625,1,21858,'base+meta_keywords_user_search'),(78626,1,21859,'base+meta_keywords_user_page'),(78627,1,21860,'base+meta_keywords_user_list'),(78630,1,21863,'ert ertert'),(78631,1,21864,'ertertertertertertertert'),(78635,1,21868,'Venues'),(78636,1,21869,'Caterers'),(78637,1,21870,'Transport'),(78638,1,21871,'Florists'),(78639,1,21872,'Beauticians'),(78640,1,21873,'Venues'),(78641,1,21874,'Tostmat